data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the vibrant community of Union Park, Wesley Chapel. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom beauty stands on a corner lot, overlooking a tranquil pond, ensuring you enjoy serenity with no rear neighbors. From the moment you approach, you're greeted by a charming covered front porch, flanked by lanterns on each side of the garage. Inside, an open floor plan illuminated by an upgraded lighting package awaits. The kitchen serves as the heart of the home, boasting stainless steel appliances, a spacious island with breakfast bar, walk-in pantry, and shimmering granite countertops. The gold handles and a chic tile backsplash add a touch of luxury. Storage and organization are enhanced with new shelving units in the pantry, laundry room, and primary bedroom closet. The home resonates with thoughtful upgrades, from tray ceilings and plantation shutters to board and batten accent walls. The primary and front bedrooms are enhanced with new fans, while the lighting package brings a warm glow. Functionality is seamlessly integrated with coded locks, a video doorbell, and prewiring for an alarm system. The primary bedroom offers two walk-in closets and a full bathroom with dual vanity sinks, a walk-in glass shower, a garden tub, and a wet closet. Outdoors, the covered and screened-in rear patio offers a perfect vantage point to the pond. Aesthetic upgrades include the removal of builder landscaping, replaced with custom designs, and new gutters for added functionality. The Union Park community is unmatched in amenities: two pools, including a lap pool, a playful splash zone, fitness center, dog park, walking trails with fitness stations, playgrounds, basketball courts, and more! Every member of the family, from the little ones to the furry ones, has a space to enjoy. Recent home updates for peace of mind include a new AC, roof, and upgraded kitchen and bathroom fixtures. With added overhead garage storage and impeccable interior enhancements, this home is the epitome of move-in ready. Experience the blend of community charm and home luxury in Wesley Chapel. Do not miss out on this opportunity and schedule your showing today!
